## Summary Report: OpenClaw Channel Plugin SDK and Telegram Plugin Structure

I've completed a thorough exploration of the OpenClaw plugin SDK and Telegram channel plugin structure. Here's a comprehensive report for your PulseBoard channel plugin planning.

