## Part 1: Plugin SDK Channel Contract Files

### Key SDK Files Located:
- `/src/plugin-sdk/channel-contract.ts` - Re-exports channel type contracts
- `/src/plugin-sdk/core.ts` - Main SDK entry, helper builders, and plugin entry system
- `/src/plugin-sdk/plugin-entry.ts` - Plugin registration API and entry helpers

### Channel Contract Re-exports (`channel-contract.ts`):

The file is minimal and re-exports core types from `src/channels/plugins/types.js`:
- `BaseProbeResult`
- `BaseTokenResolution`
- `ChannelAgentTool`
